snippet.textDisplay: The LIE that a face mask is not needed if you do not have Covid-19 is a common one.    True it will not stop an airborne virus, but it will stop droplets and most vital of all, as skin transmission is the most common way of picking this up.   Any mask prevents you from touching your mouth or nose.    The reason they downplay the mask for the non-infected is to conserve limited supply.
